.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KSHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c567%2c20220523%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSHM,111,聲,567,20220523,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"567","JDATE":"20220523","JTITLE":"聲請停止審判"}